commit.message:
Merge #10264

10264: fix: Don't seek outside of character boundaries in completion handler r=Veykril a=iDawer

Fixes #10219 panic when entering `:` in `$0` places:
```rust
fn main() {
    "⊞$0";
}
```

```rust
struct S {
    д$0 u8
}
```


Co-authored-by: Dawer <7803845+iDawer@users.noreply.github.com>

